    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Dear sir,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "I would like to submit a theory that may lead to a solution",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "of what the Flying saucers really are-these objects could",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "be Lights, caused by Radio Television Beams illuminating",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "moist vapor, not unlike phosphous on rain soaked wood in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "certain seasons-the northern lights \"Aurora Borealus\" have",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "manifested themselves for years, setting up Electro magne-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "tism & Earth potential which distorts normal Telegraph",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Communications. The lights are somewhat like a Fan & can",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "be seen as far south as Equator-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "It is my opinion that Flying Saucers are Electrically induced",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "currents onto a space (small clouds) and causing it to glow-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "this cloud being charged Electrically and a magnetic polarity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "being same as the interceptor it can never be overtaken, and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "would if persued gradually grow Dimmer & dissappear giving",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "the impression that it out distanced the persuer with a great",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Burst of speed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "This is submitted as a theory as I do not have the power",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "or facilities to prove or disprove. But I submit a suggestion",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "whereby a test could be made.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "When these saucers appear again Have the TV & all Broadcasts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "silenced from the air and check for results-this may not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
